Dummy-coded Motor maps (expect rating & outcome rating)

Model (CESeO)
  • parameter:
  • 0 Cue onset,
  • 1 ExpectationRating onset
  • 0 Stimulus onset
  • 0 pmod: expectation rating (angle)
  • 1 OutcomeRating onset
  • Motion covariate: 24DOF + CSF
  • Spike combined into one regressor (Incorrect)
